4. Make it survive reboots (“always run”)

pm2 save
pm2 startup

pm2 startup prints a sudo ... command — run that once. After that, PM2 restores your saved processes on boot.

5. Useful PM2 commands

pm2 status              # is it running?
pm2 logs gardenworld    # tail logs
pm2 restart gardenworld # after npm run build
pm2 stop gardenworld
pm2 delete gardenworld

Deploy workflow

Whenever you update the app:

npm run build
pm2 restart gardenworld

