Basic PM2 Commands
Command
Description
pm2 start app.js
Start an app
pm2 start app.js --name api
Start with custom name
pm2 list
Show all running processes
pm2 stop app_name
Stop a process
pm2 restart app_name
Restart a process
pm2 delete app_name
Remove from PM2
pm2 logs
Show logs of all apps
pm2 monit
Real-time monitoring dashboard
pm2 save
Save current processes




